gameInformation.title: Advanced UI System
gameInformation.author: dammitbird
gameInformation.description:
Advanced inventory UI

Zeldalike. Inventory UI allows you to select an item, remembers what item you have selected and where in the UI your cursor is.
It sets an active item. 

Currency system (easy) pickup money.

Pause menu

feel free to poke around
